doctype html
html(lang="en")
 head
   title Homepage
 body
  :markdown-it(linkify langPrefix='highlight-')
   # You have reached the homepage for my url shortener service!
   ## Usage
   Type a **URL** in this box or at the end of this page's _address_. You will be sent a shortened **URL** with which to use to link to your desired original **URL**!
   
   Your IP: #{client_ip} <-- Don't try any funny stuff.
 form(action='/' method='GET')
  div.form-group
   label(for='url') URL:
   input(type=text name='url')
   button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit') Submit
    